## Chapter 2 Team

* Perfect sprint team (7 people or fewer):
  1. (Decider) Someone with authority to make decisions, official decision-maker for the project.
  2. (Finance expert) Who can explain where the money comes from.
  3. (Marketing expert) Who crafts your company's messages.
  4. (Customer expert) Who regularly talks to your customers one-on-one.
  5. (Tech/logistics expert) Who best understands what your company can build and deliver.
  6. (Design expert) Who designs the products your company makes.
  7. (Facilitator) Somone who organisers the sprint.
* Schedule extra experts for Monday afternoon, during their visit they can tell the rest of the team what they know and share their opinions.
